data.description: Looking for a 4 bedroom ranch in Westlake Village? This is the one! Upgrades galore! Walk in to the entry way that looks into the expansive living room with built-ins and cathedral ceilings. The large eat-in kitchen features a great walk-in closet and slider doors opening to the freshly painted deck and beautiful back yard. The large master bedroom in complete with bathroom and walk-in closet. 2 bedrooms, another full size bathroom and laundry room complete this first floor. The large basement has recently been painted and features a 4th bedroom, bar area and plenty of room for another living space, gym, office or whatever you wish! Potential 3rd bathroom in basement as well. Roof, siding, gutters, back yard drain tile, and furnace 2021. Water heater 2018. Please see list of updates for more. Don’t miss your chance to see this home and enjoy living in this community with pool, basketball courts and newly updated golf course!
